OL,6,FSmith inhaled pure nitrogen gas
OL,7,Fthrough a face mask causing oxygen
OL,8,Fdeprivation. He appeared conscious for
OL,9,Fseveral minutes into the procedure.
OL,11,FFor at least two minutes, Smith made
OL,12,Fseizure-like movements on the gurney
OL,13,Fthat sometimes had him pulling against
OL,14,Fthe restraints.
OL,16,FThat was followed by several minutes
OL,17,Fof laboured breathing. He was
OL,18,Fpronounced dead after 22 minutes.
