OL,6,FOn Wednesday, both the and 11th
OL,7,FCircuit Court of Appeals said they
OL,8,Fwould not block the execution despite
OL,9,FSmiths' pleas for it to intervene.
OL,11,F"What effect the condemned person will
OL,12,Ffeel from the nitrogen gas itself, no
OL,13,Fone knows," Dr. Jeffrey Keller,
OL,14,Fpresident of the American College of
OL,15,FCorrectional Physicians said.
OL,17,FAlabama, along with Mississippi and
OL,18,FOklahoma, is the only US states to
OL,19,Fhave authorised the use of nitrogen
OL,20,Fhypoxia.
