OL,6,FHow did the execution work?
OL,8,FThe method is known as Nitrogen
OL,9,FHypoxia.
OL,11,FBrain cells begin to die after one
OL,12,Fminute without oxygen, and serious
OL,13,Fbrain damage is "likely" after three
OL,14,Fminutes, according to University of
OL,15,FMichigan research.
OL,17,FAfter 15 minutes without oxygen brain
OL,18,Frecovery is "virtually impossible".
